maxlen.file1: unlimited #System will determine the maximum length based on its constraints

minlen.file1: 14  #Default for password-only accounts.  MFA accounts will use a lower minimum.
minlen.file2: 8  # Minimum length for MFA-enabled accounts. 14 for password only is enforced through separate mechanism/policy, not pwquality.

dcredit.file1: 1 # Require at least one non-alphabetic character for password-only accounts.
dcredit.file2: 1  # Require at least one non-alphabetic character for password-only accounts. This is enforced through separate mechanism/policy, not pwquality.

minclass.file2: 1  #This would be set higher for password only accounts, but handled through separate mechanism.
